{"TopicId":91463,"ForumId":38,"TopicTitle":"Bad Suggestions for KSP","CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-28T12:38:29Z","PageNum":5,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"legoclone09","CreatedById":142607,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-28T20:04:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222777217\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475022624\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 hours ago, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP-themed Magic-style trading card game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat would be a cool seperate game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRock(et), plane(per), Kerbal!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Andem","CreatedById":155578,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-28T21:17:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222778375\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475091702\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022163034\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheKosanianMethod\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, TheKosanianMethod said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want weather implemented. High winds, muddy dirt is hard to land on, the runway becomes slick when it rains.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI really don\u0027t see why this would be a bad thing inherently... In fact, this sounds really fun to me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"insert_name","CreatedById":150339,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-29T00:58:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd solid fuel \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"0111narwhalz","CreatedById":110660,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-29T04:06:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMicrotransaction-limited booster count.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReturn the atmosphere to its first incarnation, wherein the density is a more-or-less constant pea soup until its surface at 70km. What? People keep complaining that reentry is too easy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-29T11:59:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd in-game anti-LV-N-engine environmentalists which besieged \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222778830\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475110716\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150339\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022insert_name\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, insert_name said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd solid fuel \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSLBM have. Not a bad suggestion at all.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"insert_name","CreatedById":150339,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-29T17:31:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222779375\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475150396\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd in-game anti-LV-N-engine environmentalists which besieged \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSLBM have. Not a bad suggestion at all.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSource? All the SLBM s I know of use thrust vectoring.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-29T18:43:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222779849\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475170312\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150339\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022insert_name\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, insert_name said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSource? All the SLBM s I know of use thrust vectoring.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E = reaction control system. Tridents and some others use a solid gas generator with several slit nozzles around. While the powder burns, nozzle firescreens aim gas jets in desired directions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ackoli","CreatedById":155697,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-30T23:20:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMICROTRANSACTIONS! GUNZ! NUKS! ALEINS! BLUD! VIOLDENCE! RAINBOWZ EVERYHWERE! MORE BLUD! MORE VIOLDENCE! TURN IT INTO A COPY OF GTA BUT WITH KERBALZ! \u00A0EVILNESS! EA! MORE STUF! STAR WARS SPACECRAFT! AND MORE EPICNARS!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222778408\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475093071\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022142607\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022legoclone09\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/28/2016 at 5:34 PM, legoclone09 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat would be a cool seperate game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRock(et), plane(per), Kerbal!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmtg does not work like that.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-10-01T15:53:53Z\u0022 title=\u002210/01/2016 03:53  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 1, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Red Iron Crown\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003ESnipped out political references.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"55delta","CreatedById":101735,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-01T04:14:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn an effort to add more realism to KSP, remove all throttle controls.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-01T04:43:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nChange 3d model of a sitting Kerbal: make it somewhat bigger.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"spacebrick3","CreatedById":158990,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-01T15:13:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd explosive consoles. Every time something goes wrong, one of the controls (navball, map, supplies, communications, etc.) will explode in a shower of sparks. To repair them, you need at least a level 5 engineer and a drill that can break through the 4th wall.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"njmksr","CreatedById":114236,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-01T15:31:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo add realism, every time a Kerbal dies, the public loses faith in your space program and you can\u0027t do anything for one (real-life) year.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd add\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Emega\u003C/strong\u003Etransactions: to launch a rocket, you have to pay as much as it would really cost. R\u0026amp;D costs included.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"njmksr","CreatedById":114236,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-02T12:18:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, I believe that the \u0027revert\u0027 option is too unrealistic. Take it out.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Technical Ben","CreatedById":10512,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-02T12:20:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP should be like real life and have the moon get bigger as it approaches the horizon. I guess this is because it is closer to the ground, right? So in KSP the Muns orbit is wrong, is should be more elliptical to be the same as on Earth...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n/sacasm (Please don\u0027t think I think that is real!)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chabadarl","CreatedById":169589,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-02T18:07:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI haven\u0027t see yet so :\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust make it an 2d arcade game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MDZhB","CreatedById":99243,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-02T19:54:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey, hey, now. Let\u0027s just keep KSP how it is and never change it ever again! That way we can all just give up on these silly \u0022ideas\u0022, and no one gets their feelings hurt!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-10-02T19:54:54Z\u0022 title=\u002210/02/2016 07:54  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 2, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by MDZhB\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RocketSquid","CreatedById":152665,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-02T22:40:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222778397\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475092726\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/28/2016 at 3:58 PM, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave gravity drop off linearly, instead of the inverse square of distance.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLinear? Why can\u0027t we just use the inverse cube?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"55delta","CreatedById":101735,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T00:33:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake SRBs one time refillable, add the ability to make solid fuel at a refinery,\u00A0and then have all vehicles start empty and require fueling.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T01:15:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInvert all gravity curves so that gravity is 0 at the center of the system and approaches infinity as you approach the edge of the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T05:16:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLet the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E crew be visible from outside, and disable the hide option.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLevel 2. Impose a fine if somebody of them gets hurted.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ackoli","CreatedById":155697,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T07:20:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI had a dream Where Jebediah kerman Exploded for no reason. make that happen ingame.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KSK","CreatedById":61025,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T07:48:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nASCII art graphics. Hey - it worked for Dwarf Fortress.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RocketSquid","CreatedById":152665,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T12:25:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222784921\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475480922\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002261025\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KSK\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, KSK said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nASCII art graphics. Hey - it worked for Dwarf Fortress.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want Kerbal Fortress now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T13:23:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... with 782 types of fuel being produced from 542 minerals.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chabadarl","CreatedById":169589,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T14:03:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEvery mod ever made come with the standard installation and you cannot remove them... And you must file a report for every bug you encounter...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}